Title: Entertaining Agents 17 Entertaining Agents  
Author: Peter Wavish 
Abstract: The Multiple Agent Systems project at Philips Research Laboratories (PRL) in Redhill, UK has developed a distinctive approach to the design and implementation of multi-agent systems and has applied it, amongst other things, to entertainment. This article explains some of the philosophy that underlies the approach. 
